Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainmentâ€™s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznaviâ€™s love?

snippet.title: Drop the Beat | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
Drop the Beat is an electrifying rap where participants, squad bosses, and judges come together to perform as one, creating an unforgettable experience. With everyone bringing their unique style and energy, the track turns into a high-energy celebration, blending voices, beats, and camaraderie for a blast that embodies unity and pure hip-hop joy.



Song Credits
Track Name: Drop the Beat
Written & Performed By: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,LashcurryRaga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna, 
Primary Artist: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar
Track Name: Drop the beat

Singer/Performed By/Cast: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Lyricist/Written By: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Lyrics


Jizzy & Talha 
Bhool Chuk Maaf First time it is.
Hume ab tak nai nikala, Good Sign it is
MTV badi ghadi samne lagado
Taki Ikka bhai can know what time it is.

Raga bhai aaya phone, Bole pocket dail hai.
EPR ki small talk bhi Rocket Science hai.
DMC ke DMS pura DHH
Friend circle ka sirf radius 8 Mile hai

Raftaar bhai is back like mihir virani
Rapper kandhe pe uthaya jaise bees litre paani
Jab dino bhai the.. naturally funny  
To hume kyun bulaya jokes marwane??

EPR
Musht-e-khaak
Khamoshi raeth si ghadiyon mein
Raqs e hasti hathkadiyon mein
Paav phisle toh daldal mein 

Barg-e-khizaan 
Fizaao mein teri himmat hai
Udne ki teri shiddat pe
Havaon ko na fursat de

charagh-e-junoon
Misl-e-Abr-e-baharon mein

Behre in badlon mein
raushni tere praharo se 

Gulshan e dahr ke kagaz ko tu awaaz de
Taqdiir-e-aasman mein siyahi teri azaad hai

Bleed ink

Raga
You know Iâ€™m all about the rage jab baat ho mere squad ki
Daabke vocal chords jazbaat nikaale opps ke
Bars so dope I get you high on my aushadhi 
Put you in a vibe in a second | sorcery 

Ye medicine vilaayti
Hum hai Home grown remedies 
Soch kratikaari like menime no feminist 
Dil ke khole raaz ye siyaahi failegi panno pe 
Ab state of mind lashcurry 
Im mad trippin pehle si hi 

Im one of the last real ones in the game 
When Iâ€™m done the itâ€™s done, Iâ€™m big pun of this game 
Iâ€™m the one who brings fun in this game 
So, this big bad man is in this building to stay

Dino 
Ye sachin sare hum yaha ke ramakanth hai
Ye mic mai aaye toh toh chote hum sama bandh de
Hai kalakar hai bade tabhi Shama mangte
Ye kmzoro ka stage nahi, ye jagah Bombay
Ye booth mai ghuse toh , sabko bhoot bana de
Ye loop mai bajengae, mic mai thgook baha ke
Hum guth mai chalte hai, aur hum loot machate
Sare brutal hai log. yeh hai grop savasher

Aditya bhai kaha hai ye toh Mai madari hai
Ye safar acha katega insane savari hai
EPR RAA IKKA RAGA DMC
AUR Shoutout to the girl,s JO YE gama chala rahi hai




Ikka
Do yaar hustle chaar 
Parkhenge ki kaun badiya kalakaar 
Hoga kaun ithihasic abki baar 
Kaun karega baaakiyon ko sabko dar kinaar
Competition or tough hoga abki baar 
Sath denge Dino dee raga Epr 
Hustle hone wala 4 gunna crazy hai 
Kyunki wapis aayeya mera bhai the og is back raftaar


Raftaar
hustle ki mehfil me swaagat taaqat likhai ki
dikhai di to kala ki janta bani himaiti
kachii kadi ki taakein hum ghadi aati vidai ki
nibhai kalakaari jisne uska pen hai mighty
tujhme kala bhari tabhi tu invited
decide hoga hustle bas missile ban tu guided
profile hogi badhi teri badhegi ab brightness
never gonna fall baawe WE STAND UNITED
KABHI JEET KABHI LOSS
NO SIDES NO TOSS
YAHAN SE GAYE TO MILNA ON TOP
THIS IS HIP HOP AND WE DONT STOP
-----

Join our team of writers as they toss around the most outlandish, over-the-top, and downright ridiculous ideas for the ultimate Diwali-themed video. From traditional family gatherings gone hilariously wrong to bizarre plot twists involving our IP's, each suggestion brings its own flavor of chaos and comedy.

snippet.title: Girls Hostel - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Minku hai bahut bada khiladi (played by Amit Bhadana) jo ek sath 3-3 girlfriends ko ghuma raha hai aur unke gifts aur paise kha raha hai. Lekin ek din Minku ki life mein aa jata hai bhuchal jab ek girlfriend uske samne rakh deti hai ek demand. Ye sabhi ladkiyan rehti hai ek hi Girls Hostel mein. Kaise bachayega Minku apni jaan? Ye jaan jaoge aap agar dekhoge ye mazedar video.

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

snippet.title: The Tri Folding Phone Durability Test! - someone has to try...
snippet.description:
The Triple Folding Smartphone From Huawei is here to be tested. Get a 4-week trial, free postage, and a digital scale at https://www.stamps.com/jerryrig. Thanks to Stamps.com for sponsoring the show! Folding smartphones and their soft flexible screens have been around for about 5 years now. Samsung has a few folding phones, Google has their Pixel fold. And now Huawei has the worlds first triple fold smartphone that is about the same size as an iPad. 
Today we are going to durability test the new tri fold smart phone called the Huawei Mate XT Ultimate Design and see how well it can hold up to every day life.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to the Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

Bhide informs everyone that the order has been cancelled, everyone tries to help him sell all the boxes of chocolates but fail to sell even a single box, just then Sonu comes home and informs everyone that someone has offered to buy all the boxes and he is coming to the society in the evening. Who is this secret angel?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #à¤¤à¤¾à¤°à¤•à¤®à¥‡à¤¹à¤¤à¤¾à¤•à¤¾à¤‰à¤²à¥à¤Ÿà¤¾à¤šà¤¶à¥à¤®à¤¾ #sonyliv #comedy #comedy2024 #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Making Halloween Costume Vlog in Tamil | Sheep Costume for Kids
snippet.description:
In this video join as I make some Halloween costumes for Alandra and Alaric. This year, I decided to get creative and make matching sheep costumes, perfect for a fun family Halloween look. Simple, affordable materials, like cotton balls and a basic dress, can be easily transform them into cute, fluffy sheep outfits.
#halloweencostume #sheepcostume #steffivlogs

Gluing cotton balls onto the dress to give it that perfect wooly sheep appearance. These homemade costumes are not only budget-friendly but also a great DIY Halloween costume idea for parents who love crafting unique and personalized outfits for their children. I hope this week's vlog inspires you to make your own homemade sheep costumes and enjoy a fun-filled crafting session with your little ones! See you soon with more interesting videos.

snippet.title: 2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN
snippet.description:
2 Minecraft Speedrunners VS TITAN. You asked for it. The return of Minecraft Manhunt, George & Dream VS a real life Titan

Follow my socials:
â½ Twitter - @dream
â½ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
â½ Snapchat - @dreampublic

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

Merch: https://www.dream.shop

All video music is custom scored and produced by Dream & PmBata. 

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt 2: TITAN TAKEDOWN. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is a massive, near invincible TITAN, being controlled by a real life human projected into the game using our custom fusion technology, instead of multiple hunters. This is the toughest challenge I have faced yet. GeorgeNotFound and I are on a team of 2, and are trying to speedrun and beat the game.

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my anonymous friend tries everything he can to stop me. This is all custom coded by us. 

If this video somehow gets 1,000,000 likes we'll announce the date of the next episode early.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt #MinecraftManhunt2
